10.1016/j.jhep.2017.12.019

LAYSUMM

TITLE

Impact of comorbidities on patient outcomes after interferon-free therapy-induced viral eradication in hepatitis C

PARAGRAPH

The prognosis of patients with severe comorbidities may not benefit from HCV viral clearance.

An algorithm to decide who will benefit from the treatment is needed to manage the chronic HCV infection better.